    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Yes this is a feature of our library, we already have some usage warning. Every widget should be very clear when used in a bad way: show the usage.\n\nThe type checking/tooling of React is very powerful, I don't think we want to recode anything here. I understand we have those \"basic\" usage exceptions but maybe we could just have a look if/how we could use the React propTypes tooling to benefit from all the features they have.\n",
